    "description": "Mission in Snowdriftland——Snowlogue，是Mission in Snowdriftland 任务的免费试玩版。欢迎免费体验前3关。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景</h2>电玩组织的总部——UPIXO发生了大混乱：可恶的坏人矮尔．屁克斯，从档案柜中偷走了电玩历史中最重要又最有价值的文物。请帮助Chubby从矮尔．屁克斯的冰封之境飘雪国里找回所有的文物吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/28aedf0e6f6ab9960adc9195df55e791.avif?t=1734819756\" width=616 height=296 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏概念</h2>飘雪國任务是一款概念独特的游戏：你能像传统的降临节日历一样玩，每天选择一個不同的关卡，让Chubby带领你欢度每個寒冷的冬日。或者你也能像玩一般的平台游戏那样，随时随地上线。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/949d791562d0edc08235405a577c89e2.poster.avif?t=1734819756\" width=616 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/949d791562d0edc08235405a577c89e2.webm?t=1734819756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/949d791562d0edc08235405a577c89e2.mp4?t=1734819756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >适合所有玩家</h2>飘雪國任务适合所有玩家：年龄层低、缺乏经验的玩家，可以在简单易懂的环境下，快速进入状况寻找文物；同时，核心玩家则要面对超酷的挑战，在每一個关卡收集24片雪花。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/12c5a3317d4b0793f342d4c3f28315a8.poster.avif?t=1734819756\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/12c5a3317d4b0793f342d4c3f28315a8.webm?t=1734819756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/12c5a3317d4b0793f342d4c3f28315a8.mp4?t=1734819756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/43b2d680cd46e928302a272c1cb0ea11.avif?t=1734819756\" width=616 height=206 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >疯狂世界</h2>你将要对抗各种古怪的敌人，像色彩鲜艳的企鹅，以及边听音乐边慢跑的北极熊！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/4996ec31221fabf3e56d34e84f44dbf8.avif?t=1734819756\" width=616 height=206 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3个关卡<br></li><li>像素艺术<br></li><li>复古配乐<br></li><li>与所有控制器兼容<br></li><li>竞速计时<br></li><li>成就</li></ul><br><strong>Chubby又要出任务了⋯⋯你会加入他的行列嗎？</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/08dcf0567e945e655bfe92371f4fa1a3.poster.avif?t=1734819756\" width=616 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/08dcf0567e945e655bfe92371f4fa1a3.webm?t=1734819756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561750/extras/08dcf0567e945e655bfe92371f4fa1a3.mp4?t=1734819756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
